    "text": "Photo by @andrea_frazzetta / An aerial view of the famous ghost town of Craco, Italy. The town has been chosen as a location for many historical movies. Abandoned in 1963 after a disastrous landslide, this village in the province of Matera, Italy, attracts thousands of tourists every year. To see more photos from my travels, follow me @andrea_frazzetta. #italy #basilicata",
